I was going to point this out.

00:52:48.490 --> 00:52:50.800
This was kind of obvious.

00:52:50.800 --> 00:52:52.860
If anybody could see that was happening.

00:52:52.860 --> 00:52:57.010
So I will tell you what you do when this
